748
01:55:43,762 --> 01:56:12,117
[SPEAKER_01]: Thank you so much to Terry and Vivian for having us, and thank you to you all for staying and listening to us.

749
01:56:16,332 --> 01:56:22,778
[SPEAKER_03]: So my first observation is that it's kind of a misnomer, the Silly Billy.

750
01:56:23,358 --> 01:56:28,942
